          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（沉醉东风） 莫不是胡贼又来相劝？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他若来时呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（沉醉东风） 拼一命丧黄泉，誓无他愿！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小番引李陵同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回避了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小番",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小番同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥在哪里？吓，啊呀哥哥吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哭相思） 怎知今日重相见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李陵，看你这般打扮，莫非走差了路了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥，小弟一言难尽！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坐了讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呀呀呸！你在此享荣华，受富贵，朝廷怎饶得你过？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀哥哥吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（江儿水） 不想朝廷怒，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 李陵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（川拨掉） 若要我折节延年，若要我折节延年，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（川拨掉） 我拼一命死在眼前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 形孤影只谁为伴？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李陵，你今日到此何干？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟此来，非为别事；只因受降城外，新筑一台，名曰望乡台，请哥哥到彼望"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李陵，你教我干别的事，断然不去，教我拜望家乡，哪有不去之理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，哥哥请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客邸思君切，家乡未得归。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欲穷千里目，更上一层台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小番甲持酒上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小番甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了，我自到此间，不食胡地之物。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是小弟自备的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼哼，好个自备的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！看云山万迭，烟树模糊，不知哪一答是我的家乡？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望南一带就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘎！望南一带就是。吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（画眉序） 阿呀！我那圣上吓！念圣主……"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，李陵，你在那里做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与哥哥同拜家乡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！你既降顺在此，那一答就不是你的家乡了。谁要你拜！没廉耻！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（画眉序） 啊呀我那圣上吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人同",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小番们把酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里差来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丁大王差来承应的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小心承应。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同回回曲） 高高山上一庙堂，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（滴溜子） 思量起，思量起，倦容怎抬？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回避了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 怎遣得愁山并闷海！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥，小弟有言告禀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。怀忠守节，虽义士之纲常；应变随机，乃达人之权度。单于这等看待，哥"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "背义忘恩，实人臣之共耻；去顺效逆，岂忠孝之所为？我苏武受汉朝三世厚恩，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥，此话非小弟之故。单于闻陵与哥哥交厚，故使小弟来说，不想哥哥是……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（铧锹儿） 受尽了千磨百灭，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这等看来，我李陵与卫律之罪，上通于天，不可容也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（铧锹儿） 我自叹嗟，徒意切。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 李陵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（铧锹儿） 你教我去顺膻羯，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还请三思。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李陵，我和你相交半世，还不晓得我的性儿么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（铧锹儿） 我若是贪图荣贵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "铁石心肠不肯移，含悲洒泪枉嗟吁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一片忠心难尽说，空中惟有老天知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥，小弟告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李陵，今后不许来看我！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自然还要来看哥哥的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！你若再来，我就一剑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没廉耻！还不走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亏你羞也不羞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏武急下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李陵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！羞死我李陵也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李陵下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
